    "about_us_custom1_84x84r": {
      "type": "about-us-custom1",
      "name": "About Us (Custom)",
      "settings": {
        "bg_color": "#fbf3cc",
        "heading_color": "#ff4d1c",
        "blob_bg_color": "#5d57c5",
        "blob_text_color": "#fbf3cc",
        "bottom_text_color": "#5d57c5",
        "heading": "ABOUT US",
        "blob_image": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_1.png",
        "blob_text": "<p>We started The Boring Foods Company because we were deeply confused about health and wellness ourselves. Everywhere we looked, there was <strong>noise, misinformation</strong> and too many <strong>trends</strong> built on fear. </p><p>The only tools we knew how to trust were the ones we’d built our lives around: asking the kind of questions that most people skip, going beyond the surface, and getting deep, rich insights. </p>",
        "sparkle_image": "shopify://shop_images/Spark_1.png",
        "sign_image": "shopify://shop_images/Gemini_Generated_Image_wa45bdwa45bdwa45-removebg-preview.png",
        "bottom_text": "<p>It’s how we met in 2019: two newly graduated 22-year-olds, freshly back from the US, working as economic development researchers in Bihar. That year taught us something important: i<strong>f you want the real story, you have to go to the source. </strong></p>"
      }
    },
    "story_with_image_7MKR8x": {
      "type": "story-with-image",
      "name": "Story with Image",
      "settings": {
        "bg_color": "#fbf3cc",
        "text_color": "#5d57c5",
        "highlight_color": "#5d57c5",
        "main_text": "<p>Years later, that same instinct pulled us back into the field in 2025, We travelled across the country armed with notebooks, questions, and a very stubborn <strong>belief</strong> that <strong>Indian ingredients deserved more respect than they were getting.</strong></p><p></p><p>We met farmers who treated their crops not as commodities but as an extension of their own identity. We also saw the parts no one talks about: sacks stored in damp godowns, produce mixed across grades, and adulterants added to pure ingredients. <br/></p>",
        "bullet_list": "<p>Slowly, a clear picture emerged:</p><ul><li>farmers were growing high-quality produce</li><li>trader and wholesaler mismanagement was letting contamination enter the supply chain</li><li>consumers who wanted to eat better couldn’t do so </li></ul>",
        "main_image": "shopify://shop_images/width_1600.webp",
        "sticker_image": "shopify://shop_images/Sun_8cabb70d-ba01-470c-9334-5a948663e3a3.png",
        "image_caption": "(somewhere in the Western Ghats)"
      }
    },
    "stamp_next_box_7cJNMT": {
      "type": "stamp-next-box",
      "name": "Stamp Text Box",
      "settings": {
        "bg_color": "#fbf3cc",
        "heading_color": "#f84b21",
        "shadow_color": "#ffc62f",
        "text_color": "#fbf3cc",
        "box_color": "#5a56b3",
        "heading": "SO WE DECIDED TO FIX IT",
        "icon_image": "shopify://shop_images/Rose.png",
        "stamp_bg_image": "shopify://shop_images/Stamp_50bc2e4c-ca4f-402f-bb41-d672d68b4a17.svg",
        "text_padding_vertical": 20,
        "text_padding_horizontal": 20,
        "text_content": "<p>We researched, tested, rejected, re-tested, and built a sourcing model that could preserve quality from soil to spoon.</p><p><strong>We didn’t want nostalgia. We wanted function.</strong></p><p>So we studied each ingredient for what it actually does, what makes it effective, and how people can use it in a way that genuinely supports their health: without drama or fear. <br/></p><p></p><p></p>"
      }
    },
    "vision_and_sigh_off_QEwPBM": {
      "type": "visionAndSighOff",
      "name": "Vision & Sign-off",
      "settings": {
        "bg_color": "#fbf3cc",
        "text_color": "#5d57c5",
        "highlight_color": "#5d57c5",
        "header_prefix": "That’s how",
        "logo_image": "shopify://shop_images/logo-web.png",
        "header_suffix": "was built.",
        "header_color": "#5d57c5",
        "vision_text": "<p>Our long-term<strong> vision</strong> is simple: <br/><strong>to make preventative, foundational health a part of everyday life. </strong></p><p>We want to build a community of people who feel informed, not overwhelmed; who read labels, ask questions, and choose what’s right for their bodies with confidence instead of fear.</p>",
        "signature_text": "<p>Keeping it boring (and better),<br/>Anvi and Varuni</p>",
        "signature_bg_image": "shopify://shop_images/Stamp_b468f9ac-d4a8-4013-bedd-7f6a94fe25cb.svg",
        "sig_bg_color": "#ffc62f",
        "sig_shadow_color": "#ec4c22",
        "sig_text_color": "#5d57c5",
        "starburst_image": "shopify://shop_images/Starburst_b12d13ae-875c-4690-b570-548a96b3924f.svg",
        "starburst_text": "<p>At the end of the day, our philosophy is boring on purpose.<br/><strong>Clean, simple ingredients.</strong> <strong>Transparent sourcing.<br/>Third-party testing</strong>. <strong>Evidence</strong> <strong>you can actually see.</strong> </p>",
        "starburst_text_color": "#5d57c5"
      }
